data.description: Welcome to this stunning first-level condo offering 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths in Mason! The kitchen has been updated with custom-designed cabinets along with updated ceramic tile flooring in the kitchen and main living areas. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, boasting not one, but two walk-in closets. Every bedroom in the home offers a walk in closet. Relax and unwind in the spacious living area, flooded with natural light. Step outside onto your private patio, where you can enjoy serene moments surrounded by lush greenery and plenty of outdoor space for entertaining guests or simply soaking up the sun. This condo also offers practical upgrades and well maintained medicinal systems. As part of the community, you'll have access to fantastic amenities, including a swimming pool and tennis court, perfect for staying active and socializing with neighbors.Don't miss this opportunity to make this exceptional property your own! Schedule your showing today!
